{"tid":1795280,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"CJE&M繼續擴大版圖 2020年坐擁五代兩男團","createTime":"2019-12-23T18:37:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-24T14:17:59.000Z","uid":222605,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"359c61588c4b0b78bc4393062eae8b88a5192687","tid":1795280,"uid":222605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T18:37:06.000Z","msg":"正當大家以為pd101造假係CJE&amp;M最大野心<br />\n少年，你太年輕了<br />\n2020年CJE&amp;M將會邁向新嘅高峰<br />\n<br />\nCJ旗下將會冒起兩個新男團<br />\n一個係jellyfish旗下嘅verivery<br />\n另一個係同big hit合作嘅新男團<br />\n點解會得出呢個答案<br />\n以下會詳細解釋<br />\n<br />\n首先<br />\nCJE&amp;M坐擁jellyfish 51%股份<br />\n而且對旗下男團verivery投入相當多資源<br />\nMnet出道舞台 使用頂級男/女團佈景<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/9zSZqcvRx0w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F9zSZqcvRx0w&d=IuE3y9gLaM%2BC%2BJZgSaDlpjsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=e65f71f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/9zSZqcvRx0w</a><br />\n<br />\n打歌服絕對唔差<br />\nCJ協助下 享受pre-debute舞台<br />\n親生仔級嘅待遇<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖則今年呢隊野喺樂壇回響唔大<br />\n但最近釋出預告<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/IHyb-Fc0w18\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FIHyb-Fc0w18&d=IuE3y9gLaM%2BC%2BJZgSaDlpjsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=543449b3\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/IHyb-Fc0w18</a><br />\n<br />\nYouTube油管反應唔錯<br />\n預計2020年頭將會強勢回歸<br />\n估計明年內能夠收獲一批粉絲<br />\n進入上升期<br />\n<br />\n其次<br />\nCJE&amp;M同big hit開咗間新公司<br />\n叫Belift Lab<br />\nCJ佔有52%股份<br />\n招募新男團成員<br />\n由房時赫擔任總製作人<br />\n2020年出道<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n預計兩男團會係五代男團有舉足輕重嘅地位<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fab467d7c53505eab9a917d51580926359fb323","tid":1795280,"uid":88491,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T19:27:46.000Z","msg":"樓主咁有心